## Import



Using `pulumi import`, import WAF Geo Match Set using their ID. For example:

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:waf/geoMatchSet:GeoMatchSet example a1b2c3d4-d5f6-7777-8888-9999aaaabbbbcccc
```
